A short script making use of the wiimote through pywiiuse

Init
----

Make sure you have a ipythonrc-project file in your ~/.ipython directory

    include ipythonrc

    execfile localipythonrc.py


Retrieve or update pywiiuse sources.

    git submodule init
    git submodule sync


Execution
---------

run

 $ ipython -p project example.py
